/* The join-room flow is now server-authoritative. When you choose "Join a public/private room" from the
server-pushed lobby menu, the server pushes the room list (and, for private rooms, asks for the
password via the askinput directive); the client just renders and replies. The old client-rendered
join_room_menu() / get_room_list() were removed; see menu.nvgt (push_join_list) + net.nvgt on the server. */
